              <text>The heading to Part 11 is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">and other Orders in Council</emphasis></amend.in> and substituting <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">, other Orders in Council, and rules</emphasis></amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
        </prov.body>
